  "title": "Project Director",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage client relations, consultants, and government stakeholders</li><li>Oversee budgeting, procurement, and contract administration</li><li>Monitor timelines, construction progress, and critical path activities</li><li>Lead end-to-end project execution for large-scale construction (from inception to completion)</li><li>Drive site performance, quality control, and risk management</li><li>Ensure safety compliance and lead incident investigations</li><li>Mentor and evaluate site team performance with clear KPIs</li><li>Ensure adherence to all regulatory and environmental standards</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; ram@deshingroup.com, wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>",
